;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-panel-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-panel_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation news\">Jha, Dhirendra K. (2 August 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scroll.in/article/672545/RSS-sets-up-panel-to-supervise-saffronisation-of-education/\">\"RSS sets up panel to supervise saffronisation of education\"</a>. <i>scroll.in</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-11-14</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=scroll.in&amp;rft.atitle=RSS+sets+up+panel+to+supervise+saffronisation+of+education&amp;rft.date=2014-08-02&amp;rft.aulast=Jha&amp;rft.aufirst=Dhirendra+K.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F672545%2FRSS-sets-up-panel-to-supervise-saffronisation-of-education%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AShiksha+Sanskriti+Utthan+Nyas\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-command-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-command_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/narendra-modi-bjp-smriti-irani-pmo-defence-piyush-goyal/1/399463.html\">\"In command and control\"</a>. <i>India Today</i>. 6 November 2014<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-11-14</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=India+Today&amp;rft.atitle=In+command+and+control&amp;rft.date=2014-11-06&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Findiatoday.intoday.in%2Fstory%2Fnarendra-modi-bjp-smriti-irani-pmo-defence-piyush-goyal%2F1%2F399463.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AShiksha+Sanskriti+Utthan+Nyas\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Sangh-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Sangh_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/sangh-sets-up-panel-to-push-saffronisation-of-education-114072601164_1.html\">\"Sangh sets up panel to push `saffronisation' of education\"</a>. <i>Business Standard</i>. 27 July 2014<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-11-14</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Business+Standard&amp;rft.atitle=Sangh+sets+up+panel+to+push+%60saffronisation%27+of+education&amp;rft.date=2014-07-27&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcurrent-affairs%2Fsangh-sets-up-panel-to-push-saffronisation-of-education-114072601164_1.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AShiksha+Sanskriti+Utthan+Nyas\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-blueprint-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-blueprint_8-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.firstpost.com/india/preparing-blueprint-indianise-education-dinanath-batra-1644407.html\">\"Preparing a blueprint to `Indianise' education: Dinanath Batra\"</a>. <i>Firstpost</i>. 1 August 2014<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-11-14</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Firstpost&amp;rft.atitle=Preparing+a+blueprint+to+%60Indianise%27+educa